comments: Kleber (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt before cleanly blocking Barton's (DEN) shot.
Kleber (DAL) and Barton (DEN) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
During the screen, Harris (DEN) and Curry (DAL) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Murray (DEN) as he disengages from the pick.
Curry (DAL) initiates some contact with Harris (DEN) during his drive, but the contact is marginal and does not affect Harris's ability to defend.
Jokic (DEN) is imminently actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Jokic (DEN) and Curry (DAL) make incidental contact off ball.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Porzingis (DAL) makes marginal contact with Murray's (DEN) body during his shooting motion before Kleber (DAL) cleanly blocks his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending is overturned to a blocked shot by Kleber (DAL).
Porzingis (DAL) sets the pick in Harris's (DEN) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Millsap (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Millsap (DEN) collapses his arm to his body while jumping vertically, and his body turns only after contact occurs with Doncic (DAL) during the driving shot attempt.
Harris (DEN) sets the screen in Kleber's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Doncic (DAL) extends his leg and makes contact with the ball.
Jokic (DEN) sets the pick in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Kleber (DAL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Jokic (DEN) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Barton (DEN) and Curry (DAL) briefly engage and make incidental contact with one another during the inbound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Jokic (DEN) is last to touch the ball before it goes out of play.
Harris (DEN) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Millsap (DEN) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, then lifts his left foot and returns it to the floor before passing.
Porzingis (DAL) wraps Millsap (DEN) during the inbound.
During the pick, Finney-Smith (DAL) holds Jokic (DEN) and affects his FOM.
Millsap (DEN) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith (DAL) as he disengages from the pick.
Kleber (DAL) clamps Jokic's (DEN) arm and affects his ability to get to the rebound.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
